{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Welcome to Farmer's Defence 2</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It's all very simple:\u00a0</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Plow the ground</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Buy Seeds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Sow the seeds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Water the growing plants</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Harvest them at the right moment</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Sell your Fresh Plants</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Become Rich</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But then there are the weeds:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Creeping and Spreading throughout your farm</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Destroying\u00a0 your precious plants</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Growing thicker and more difficult to destroy</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Becoming more aggressive over time</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are tools in the shop to help you fight them off.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">How much money can you make before they take over your farm completely?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">What's New In Farmer's Defence 2 ?</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Better Graphics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Improved User Interface</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">3 Difficulty Levels</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">10 types of plants with varying growth, rotting, value, and resilience.\u00a0</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Weeds that spread more aggressively over time.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fertilizers to increase the value of your plants.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Herbicides to fend off the weeds better.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">3 Tiers of tools for better upgrades.</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.